16 NEW SECTION. Section 4. Enforcement -- penalty. A violation of a provision of [sections 1 through
17 4] is an unfair or deceptive trade practice under Title 30, chapter 14, part 2, and the penalties provided in 30-14-
18 224(1) apply.
19
20 NEW SECTION. Section 5. Effective date. [This act] is effective January 1, 2026.
